{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Even if you\u2019re a beginner, you can practice your skills and master the art of renovation. From a simple paint job to a complete renovation, you can do it all. If you\u2019re not feeling the career mode, no problem. Jump into the creative mode and just chill and listen to music while repainting and redecorating your way to nirvana.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Still looking for the house of your dreams? Find or build one and make it your own. Give it the look and feeling you\u2019ve always wanted.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Roadmap:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Our game is currently in early access and still has much to be added. Below is a simplified road map of the features and assets to be added.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Gardening assets and features.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 New houses for creative mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Christmas assets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Asian assets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Victorian/Medieval assets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Painting system update.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Career mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">o\u00a0\u00a0 From simple jobs to complete renovations inside and out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">o\u00a0\u00a0 Purchase houses to renovate and sell or keep for yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">o\u00a0\u00a0 Purchase property and build a house from the ground up to sell or keep for yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 House construction/destruction system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Showrooms to visit and interact with product selection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Many, many more assets to be added.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 VR Support.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">More details are in the discussion forums.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726460/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728789936","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726460/page.bg.jpg?t=1728789936","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726460/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728789936","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726460/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728789936","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"HDR available","id":61},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Even if you\u2019re a beginner, you can practice your skills and master the art of renovation. From a simple paint job to a complete renovation, you can do it all. If you\u2019re not feeling the career mode, no problem. Jump into the creative mode and just chill and listen to music while repainting and redecorating your way to nirvana.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Still looking for the house of your dreams? Find or build one and make it your own. Give it the look and feeling you\u2019ve always wanted.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Roadmap:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Our game is currently in early access and still has much to be added. Below is a simplified road map of the features and assets to be added.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u